T02TD3460E:114b-0: @114b # // rgya gar skad du b'a g'a s'a dha nam /
T02TD3460E:114b-4: nyes pa'i dri 'joms dpal ldan rdo rje chos //
T02TD3460E:114b-5: ngag gi dkyil 'khor 'od zer dra ba 'phro //
T02TD3460E:114b-6: rdzogs sangs rgyas kun gyi gsung gi rang bzhin la //
T02TD3460E:114b-7: phyag 'tshal nas ni ngag gi sgrub thabs bshad //
T02TD3460E:114b-8: mkhas pas brtson 'grus rlung gis rab bskyod nas //
T02TD3460E:114b-9: sngags kyi rang bzhin rnam dag gzugs brjod cing //
T02TD3460E:114b-10: 'jig rten tshogs pa 'dir nams sgyu ma dang //
T02TD3460E:114b-11: smig rgyu chu zla'i rtog pa bzhin dub sgom //
T02TD3460E:114b-12: pam yig sa bon las byung sna tshogs pad //
T02TD3460E:114b-13: bsgom bya rnam par dag pa kun gyi gzugs //
T02TD3460E:114b-14: aam yig las skyes 'od zer mtha' yas pa //
T02TD3460E:114b-15: rnam dag zla ba cha shas kun rdzogs pa //
T02TD3460E:114b-16: slar yang gsang ba mchog gyur dag pa yi //
T02TD3460E:114b-17: sa bon yi ge 'od zer dra ba 'gyed //
T02TD3460E:114b-18: bandhu'i me tog 'od zer dang mtshungs pa'i //
T02TD3460E:114b-19: ngag gi spros pa brkyang mdzad rgyu gcig po //
T02TD3460E:114b-20: sa bon las byung skyon du ma gyur ba'i //
T02TD3460E:115a-0: @115a * // ting 'dzin phyag rgya tshim mdzad padma'i phyag / brtse bas mngon dga' rdo rje'i gdan la bzhugs //
T02TD3460E:115a-1: rdo rje'i chags pa dpal ldan yongs dag chags //
T02TD3460E:115a-2: ba spu'i khung bu las byung sangs rgyas kyi //
T02TD3460E:115a-3: sprin tshogs dra ba 'gro la phan par mdzad //
T02TD3460E:115a-4: 'gro ba rnams kyi rang bzhin thams cad kyang //
T02TD3460E:115a-5: shin tu rnam dag blo yis bsgom par bya //
T02TD3460E:115a-6: snying gar zla ba'i dkyil du rdo rje yi //
T02TD3460E:115a-7: 'od zer dra bas 'jig rten kun gsal blta //
T02TD3460E:115a-8: mgon po h'um yig las ni skyes gyur pa //
T02TD3460E:115a-9: sku lnga'i bdag nyid las byung sangs rgyas sprin //
T02TD3460E:115a-10: de dbus rtse mo 'phro ba'i me yi khrod //
T02TD3460E:115a-11: sku gnas srid pa gsum po snang bar mdzad ;
T02TD3460E:115a-12: /'byung po'i rgyud kyi sdug bsngal kun khyab rnams //
T02TD3460E:115a-13: yi ge chen pos gang ba rnam par 'joms //
T02TD3460E:115a-14: brjod pa rab mdzes 'od zer gyis khyab pas //
T02TD3460E:115a-15: dri med nyi ma 'char ka dga' bas chags //
T02TD3460E:115a-16: ljags skyes legs gsung shes rab mchog gi sprin //
T02TD3460E:115a-17: rdo rje las byung sdig pa rnam par 'joms ;
T02TD3460E:115a-18: / de yi rtse mor g-yo zhing rab chags pa'i //
T02TD3460E:115a-19: 'od zer rgya chen de nyid bsam par bya//
T02TD3460E:115a-20: bdag gi brtson 'grus mthu yis gzhan zil gnon //
T02TD3460E:115a-21: mchog gi mthu ldan rgol ba nges par 'joms //
T02TD3460E:115a-22: skad cig la goms stobs la skyes gyur pa //
T02TD3460E:115a-23: ngag 'grub dngos grub rnams ni nyer thob 'gyur //
T02TD3460E:115a-24: tshigs bcad rkyang pas rtag tu smra 'gyur zhing //
T02TD3460E:115a-25: rnal 'byor bstan bcos sna tshogs rig pa dang //
T02TD3460E:115a-26: bstan bcos sna tshogs nges par rtsom 'gyur zhing //
T02TD3460E:115a-27: rang nyid 'gro ba'i ched du don chen 'gyur //
T02TD3460E:115a-28: gzhan gyi sems kyis 'jug pa'ang 'du shes 'gyur //
T02TD3460E:115a-29: chags sogs sdig pa rnams kyang de yis 'joms //
T02TD3460E:115a-30: de la ting 'dzin brtan pa thob gyur nas //
T02TD3460E:115a-31: shin tu phra zhing rno 'phro nges pa yis //
T02TD3460E:115a-32: sangs rgyas go 'phang kun thob gzugs 'dzin 'gyur //
T02TD3460E:115a-33: de dag 'dir ni rnam par spyad bya min //
T02TD3460E:115a-34: rnal 'byor goms par gyur na skyes bu yi //
T02TD3460E:115a-35: 'byung dang ma byung ba rnams mdun gnas 'gyur ;
T02TD3460E:115a-36: /'dod pas 'khrugs bzhin dga' zhing chags pa yis //
T02TD3460E:115a-37: sems kyi rjes 'jug sbyor ba dang ldan gyur //
T02TD3460E:115a-38: 'di byas bdag gis dge ba nyer bsags gang //
T02TD3460E:115a-39: 'gro rnams rgyal ba'i dpal mchog 'dzin gyur cig / ri bong 'dzin pa'i 'od zer nye ba yis //
T02TD3460E:115b-0: mya ngan zug rngu yid 'jigs dang @115b 'bral shog / rgyun mi 'chad pas dge la yid chags pas //
T02TD3460E:115b-1: blo mchog las rnyed bde ba'i man ngag gi //
T02TD3460E:115b-2: rang bzhin 'di yis padma'i rigs 'jug cing //
T02TD3460E:115b-3: dpal ni rjes 'jug ting nge 'dzin dga' bar nges //
T02TD3460E:115b-4: bdag kyang legs pa'i skye bo srid rtse 'dis //
T02TD3460E:115b-5: 'bar ba'i phreng ba'i dbus kyi skur gyur cig / bla ma mchog gi brtse bas thod phreng gi //
T02TD3460E:115b-6: chu 'dzin gyis gang mngon rol dpal tshogs shog / ngag gi sgrub thabs mchog gyur pa //
T02TD3460E:115b-7: skye bo bzang pos legs sbyar ba //
T02TD3460E:115b-8: 'di yis ngag ni bsgrubs byas nas //
T02TD3460E:115b-9: ngag gi dbang phyug thob par shog /
T02TD3460E:115b-10: ngag gi sgrub thabs rdzogs so //
